data.description: PRICED TO SELL!!!!!  SELLER REQUESTS QUICK CLOSING DATE.  Originally a ranch this charming home was renovated in 2012 and is just the home you have been waiting for!  Offers open floor plan with so many possibilities for the family and even extended family.  First floor offers a sunken family room with barn doors and a charming wood burning fireplace with built in shelving.  There is a 1/2 bathroom right off the 2 car garage offering a large sunken sink.  A large living room with bay windows.  Hardwood floors throughout the first floor with the exception of the tile in living room.  Absolutely stunning kitchen with custom cabinets, granite countertops, large center island, recessed lighting and relatively new stainless-steel appliances.  Offers a large dining room for the family dinners and nestled in between the kitchen and dining room you will find extended family quarters with a separate entrance which is handicap accessible, complete with large walk-in closet/dressing area, and full ADA bathroom with washer and dryer.  Outside features a patio & fenced in yard.  Upstairs includes the master bedroom, large walk-in closet and master bathroom.  Also includes 3 large bedrooms with great closet space and additional full bathroom plus a laundry room.  Basement is fully finished with walk out egress.  Offers plenty of additional living space for your home office, gym, additional living space plus 2 large walk-in closets offering lots of storage.  Schedule your showing today!
